reviewText:
A sister kills herself in the 1950's giving herself an abortion with a knitting needle. Bill didn't want to marry her. Fifty years later another sorority takes over the house...Ouija board....boys... angry ghost.

The house had red lights in every room or else they used a red filter. The camera angle was titled and incredibly out of focus. The film was short and pointless. Not watchable.

Guide: F-word. No sex or nudity. Part of a Scream Queen 5-pack $3.74 US Walmart
